                    <p>From office lunches to weddings, we serve groups of 10 to 1,000+.</p>
                    <form id="cateringForm">
                        <div class="form-grid">
                            <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" required>
                            <input type="email" placeholder="Email Address" required>
                            <select class="full-width">
                                <option>Event Type</option>
                                <option>Corporate</option>
                                <option>Wedding</option>
                                <option>Party</option>
                            </select>
                            <input type="number" placeholder="Guest Count">
                            <input type="date">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-red full-width">Request a Catering Quote →</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">✅ Response within 24 hours guaranteed</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: var(--charcoal); color: white; text-align: center;">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--gold); width: 100px; margin: 0 auto 30px;">
                <h2 style="font-style: italic; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4;">
                    "We didn't set out to build a restaurant chain. We set out to make a difference in every person who walked through our doors."
                </h2>
                <p style="margin-top: 20px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700;">— S. Truett Cathy, Founder</p>
                <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--gold); width: 100px; margin: 30px auto 0;">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="locations" class="location-finder reveal">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Find Your Chick-fil-A</h2>
            <div class="search-box">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Enter zip code or city...">
                <button class="btn btn-red" style="padding: 10px 30px;">Search</button>
            </div>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" id="detectLocation" style="color: var(--primary-red); font-weight: 600;">
                <i class="fas fa-location-arrow"></i> Use my current location
            </a>

            <div class="location-cards">
                <div class="loc-card">
                    <h4>Peachtree City, GA</h4>
                    <p>0.4 miles · Drive-Thru ✅</p>
                    <p>Open until 10:00 PM</p>
                    <div style="margin-top: 15px; display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                        <button class="btn btn-ghost" style="padding: 8px 15px; font-size: 14px;">Directions</button>
                        <button class="btn btn-red" style="padding: 8px 15px; font-size: 14px;">Order Here</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="loc-card">
                    <h4>Fayetteville, GA</h4>
                    <p>1.2 miles · Drive-Thru ✅</p>
